        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer18707070" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13726336614098481022">I think Divakurani&apos;s short stories are genius-but she ought to lay off the novels. The book wasn&apos;t terrible, but there were some ATROCIOUS anachronisms sprinkled throughout and the heavy handed feminism was a bit much. It definitely gained in narrative voice as the plot progressed. <br/><br/>Interesting read, but wait for the paperback, or get it out of the library. </span>
  <span id="freeText13726336614098481022" style="display:none">I think Divakurani's short stories are genius-but she ought to lay off the novels. The book wasn't terrible, but there were some ATROCIOUS anachronisms sprinkled throughout and the heavy handed feminism was a bit much. It definitely gained in narrative voice as the plot progressed. <br /><br />Interesting read, but wait for the paperback, or get it out of the library. </span>
